overview: Captain Toadie: The Rocketeer Rocker is an experimental sci-fi, no-wave musical that interrogates notions of familial responsibility, celebrification, and metaphysical properties (of space and of outer space and of objects). These topics are addressed through an absurdist and amateurish use of cinematic language, which emphasizes a direct and earnest creative engagement.
title: Captain Toadie: The Rocketeer Rocker
